<h2><a name="partnering_with_us"></a>Working with <%=aname%></h2>
<p><a name="displaying_ratings"></a><span class="subhead_plain_bold">How do I install <%=aname%> widgets on my site?</span>
We offer hundreds of Web widgets, featuring quality news and opinions on important topics, from U.S. Congress to the war in Iraq. Anyone can add our widgets to their site in just minutes. Our widgets are updated hourly and come in many different sizes and formats, to fit any web style. <%=aname%> widgets are free to individuals and nonprofit organizations. To find out more, check our <%= link_to 'widgets page', "/widgets" + (params[:popup] ? '" target="_blank' : "") %>.</p>

<p><a name="writing_about_<%=aslug%>"></a><span class="subhead_plain_bold">I am a journalist and would like to write about <%=aname%>. Who do I talk to?</span>
If you are a journalist and would like to blog or write about this project, please email us at <%= mail_to email_addr("press"), email_addr("press"), :subject => "#{aname} press request", :encode => "javascript" %>.</p>

<p><a name="our_content_on_<%=aslug%>"></a><span class="subhead_plain_bold">I work for a news organization. Who do I talk to about our news content on <%=aname%>?</span>
Please email us at <%= mail_to email_addr("sources"), email_addr("sources"), :subject => "#{aname} source request", :encode => "javascript" %>. We're pleased to work with individual publishers to ensure your content is appropriately represented in <%=aname%>.</p>

<p><a name="media_partnerships"></a><span class="subhead_plain_bold">Is <%=aname%> interested in partnerships with other media companies?</span>
Absolutely. Our business model is to license our news rating services to a wide range of partners, so they may offer <%=aname%> to their own customers. To find out more, check our <%= link_to 'partner page', "/partners/" + (params[:popup] ? '" target="_blank' : "") %> or email us at <%= mail_to email_addr("partners"), email_addr("partners"), :subject => "#{aname} partner request", :encode => "javascript" %>. We'd love to hear from you.</p>

<p><a name="school_partnerships"></a><span class="subhead_plain_bold">Can my school use <%=aname%> for educational purposes?</span>
Yes, we'd love to have your school use <%=aname%>. We are starting to partner with a few good journalism schools to integrate <%=aname%> into their educational experience. If you are an educator and would like to use <%=aname%> to teach journalism in your school, please email us at <%= mail_to email_addr("partners"), email_addr("partners"), :subject => "#{aname} education request", :encode => "javascript" %>. We believe our service can help propagate journalistic "best practices" and high standards to the next generation of news professionals.</p>

<p><a name="suggestions"></a><span class="subhead_plain_bold">I have suggestions for how <%=aname%> can be improved. Who can I tell?</span>
We're always interested in hearing suggestions from our members about improving <%=aname%>. So please let us know what you think in our Feedback page, which you can join at anytime by clicking "Feedback" in the bottom navbar. Or you can email us at <%= mail_to email_addr("suggestions"), email_addr("suggestions"), :subject => "#{aname} Improvement Suggestion", :encode => "javascript" %>.</p>
